{% elif baka.last_baka_animation and baka.last_baka_animation != "" %}
### Physical State (Baka Motion — Recent)
{% set anim = baka.last_baka_animation %}
{% if anim == "BackHug" or anim == "FrontHug" %}
- Was recently held in an embrace by {{ baka.last_baka_partner }}. Physical warmth of contact may linger; emotional tone depends on how they feel about them.
{% elif anim == "BackHugMolest" %}
