- Was just kissed by {{ baka.last_baka_partner }}. The intimacy is fresh — still processing the emotion of it.
{% elif anim == "ForcedKiss" %}
- Was forcibly kissed by {{ baka.last_baka_partner }}. The violation is recent and raw. Anger, shame, or fear colors everything right now.
{% elif anim == "TouchBreasts" or anim == "SuckBreasts" %}
- Was touched intimately by {{ baka.last_baka_partner }}. Residual physical awareness; emotional reaction depends on whether this was welcomed.
{% elif anim == "ExaminePrivates" or anim == "PlayPrivates" %}
