{% elif anim == "OralOnTarget" %}
- Received intimate oral contact from {{ baka.last_baka_partner }}. Physical sensation is recent; emotional context defines how they carry it.
{% elif anim == "Spanking" or anim == "WombHit" %}
- Was struck by {{ baka.last_baka_partner }}. Sting or pain is still present. Mood affected by humiliation, anger, or residual fear.
{% elif anim == "Flirt" %}
